<table width=100%>
<tr>
<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Bran Cruento</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-02-17 12:42:24</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Yes it is a quest.  The quest is issued in the Temple of<BR>
Solesk Ro.  You will need a mask of shadow from shadowmen.<BR>
Globe of Shadow from Nokta Shaman in Lower Guk. Werebat wing<BR>
from werebat in Unrest. And a large shadowsilk obtained <BR>
through tailoring.</font></td></tr></table>
<BR>
<table width=100%>
<tr>
<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Snapp Shadowbound</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-02-24 08:38:04</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>I am a tailor and have made quite alot of money of doing shadow silk for players doing this quest.<BR>
To do the shadow silk you need:<BR>
<BR>
1 Silk swatch (2 combined spider silks)<BR>
1 gather shadow spell<BR>
2 shadow wolf pelts<BR>
<BR>
To make them easy you need a skill of arround 40<BR>
to be successfull. The most expensive items in this<BR>
process are the spells. Costs arround 5pp each,<BR>
depending of your charm.<BR>
<BR>
Good Luck</font></td></tr></table>
